CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 23, 1961, p.16, reads: "LOENDI WEEK FORMAL - As a fitting climax to the second annual Loendi Club Week, a gay formal was held last Saturday at the beautiful club, featuring the music of Bobby Jones....The next photograph shows Mrs. Willie Owens, Mr. Owens, Mrs. Herman Hill, Mr. Hill and James Goode." -- Harris Photos
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of three women and four men, including Mrs. Owens, Willie Owens, Fran Hill, Herman Hill, James Goode, unknown woman, and unknown man, posed behind bar at Loendi Club
